title: Jim Carrey's Late Girlfriend Cathriona White Married to Someone Else At Time of Death (Report)
text: Jim Carrey‘s late on again/off again girlfriend Cathriona White was married at the time of her apparent suicide, ET has confirmed. It is being reported that the coroner’s office will not be releasing her remains until she is claimed by her husband, who is her next of kin. Jim is reportedly not the husband, but [...] »
